Lips App - Know Your Lip Type

Unveil the beauty of your lips with the Lips App, your ultimate tool for classifying lip types. This innovative app leverages advanced artificial intelligence to provide insightful analyses on your lip structure, simply by taking or selecting a close-up photo. Whether you're exploring different lip shapes or seeking to celebrate the uniqueness of your own, Lips App is the perfect companion for your self-discovery journey.
